transcripts.text: Thank you.  Hi everyone!  Welcome back to the Natuber TV channel.  For those who don't know, I am the Natuber and I am from Greece. And with these videos, I make new video compilation to share these important infos with all of you.  because I think the content that I share is very useful and important for most of us.
